\id COL - SYN- Siyin Bible
\h COLOSSAE
\toc1 COLOSSAE
\toc2 Colossae
\toc3 Col
\mt1 COLOSSAE
\mt3 Laithak
\mt2 Colossians
\c 1
\s1 Paupuina
\p 
\v 1 Pathian deina tungtawn in Jesus Christ i sawltak Paul le i suapui pa Timothy,
\p 
\v 2 Colossae a om mithiangtho te le Christ sungah a thuman suapui te: I Pa Pathian le Topa Jesus Christ tung pan in thuthiamna le thinnopna note tungah hong om tahen.
\s1 Lungdamko le Thunget
\p 
\v 3 Pathian le i Topa Jesus Christ i Pa tung ah,
\p 
\v 4 Christ Jesus sungah na upna uh le mithiangtho theampo tungah na nei uh itna thu ka zak uh pan kipan in, lungdam ko in, thu kong ngetsak tawntung uh hi.
\p 
\v 5 Banghangziam cile vantung sia note atu a ki koi lametna hi a, nidang in lungdamna thupha thuman thu na za zo uh hi;
\p 
\v 6 Tua lungdamna thupha na za uh a, Pathian thuthiamna sia thuman taw na heak uh ni pan kipan, leitung theampo ah a thet bangma in, note tungah zong hong theng hi; taciang note sungah a nga bang in leitung theampo ah zong nga pha nga hi:
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Col 4:12; Philmn 1:23\x*Ka it uh sila le ka nasep pui Epaphras tung pan zong na sin sa uh bangma in, ama sia note atu in a thuman Christ i naseam a hihi;
\p 
\v 8 Ama in Thaa sungah note i itna thu zong kote tungah hong pualak zo hi.
\p 
\v 9 Hi thu hang in kote zong, note i thu ka zak uh ni pan kipan, thaa lam telthiamna le ciimna sungah, Ama deina heakna taw na kidim thei natu uh deisakna ahizong;
\p 
\v 10 Tabang in Topa lungkimsakna taw a ki phu in na nuntak thei natu uh ahizong, nasep pha khatsim sungah tampitak na nga thei natu uh le Pathian heakna sungah na khanto thei natu uh ahizong;
\p 
\v 11 Ama i a vanglian minthanna bang in, hatna theampo taw hong thahatsak tu a, thuakzawkna le thinsauna theampo sungah lungdamna taw na kidim thei natu uh ahizong, note atu tatsat ngawl in thu ka ngen tawntung uh hi;
\p 
\v 12 Khuavak sungah mithiangtho te i ngamh a lua pui te a hi tu in hong vawt Pathian tungah lungdam ka ko hi:
\p 
\v 13 Ama in khuazing i thuneina pan in kong suaktasak zo a, a it a Tapa i ukna sungah hong khin zo hi:
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Eph 1:7\x*Tapa sungah a thisan tungtawn in tatkhiatna le maw maisakna i nei hi:
\s1 Na Theampo i Tungah Lutang
\p 
\v 15 Ama sia a ki mu thei ngawl Pathian i lim le meal hi a, a ki piangsak theampo sungah tapa upa bel a hihi:
\p 
\v 16 Banghangziam cile Ama tungtawn in na theampo piangsak zo hi, vantung a om na theampo le leitung a om theampo, a ki mu thei le a ki mu thei ngawl na theampo, kumpi tokhum te, ukna te, thuneina te, vangletna te le na theampo te sia Ama in piangsak zo a, taciang Ama atu a hihi:
\p 
\v 17 Taciang Ama sia na theampo om ma in om zo a, na theampo sia Ama tungtawn in kip hi.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Eph 1:22,23\x*Ama sia pumpi a kici pawlpi i lutang a hihi: Ama sia a kipatcilna hi a, na theampo sungah Ama sia tungnungbel a hi thei natu in, thina pan tapa upa bel a hihi.
\p 
\v 19 Banghangziam cile Tapa sungah na theampo a cing in a omtu sia Pathian i lungkimna a hihi;
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Eph 2:16\x*Taciang Ama tungtawn in leitung a om nate le vantung a om nate theampo sia Ama tungah, thinglamte tung a thisan tungtawn in kilemna vawt hi.
\p 
\v 21 Taciang note, Pathian taw na kikhen uh a, nasep phangawl te hang in na thinsung uh ah Pathian i ngal te na hi ngei uh hi,
\p 
\v 22 Ahihang tu in, note sia a thiangtho, a ki mawsiat thei ngawl le ki tek kul ngawl in Ama mai ah piak tu in a pumpi thina tungtawn in kilemna vawt zo hi:
\p 
\v 23 A kip le a kho in upna sungah hong zom zo a, na zak uh lungdamna thupha lametna pan na ki khin bua uh ahile, tua lungdamna thupha sia van nuai ah a ki piangsak na theampo tung a ki pualak thu a hihi; tua mun ah keima Paul sia Pathian naseam tu in hong vawt hi;
\s1 Pawlpi atu Paul Nasepna
\p 
\v 24 Tu in note atu ka thuakna te sungah ka lungdam hi, tua thu sia a kisam lai Christ i haksatna te sia pawlpi a kici a pumpi atu in keima pumpi sungah ka dimsak hi:
\p 
\v 25 Pathian thu a khuangkhim natu in Pathian i nasep note atu hongpiak bang in, Pathian naseam in hong vawt zo hi;
\p 
\v 26 Khang tampi sung a ki phualseal thuku sia tu in Ama mithiangtho te tungah hong kilangsak zo hi:
\p 
\v 27 Hi a tuanngen thuku i hauna sia mithiangtho te tung pan Gentile mite tungah Pathian in hesak nuam hi; tua thu sia note sungah a om Christ hi a, minthanna i a lametna a hihi:
\p 
\v 28 Christ Jesus sungah mi theampo picing in hongpiak thei natu ciimna theampo taw mi theampo sia kidopna pia in ka hil uh hi:
\p 
\v 29 Tua thu sia keima zong Ama vangletna bang in na ka seam hi, tua vangletna in ka sungah thahattak in na seam hi.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Banghangziam cile note le Laodicea a omte ahizong, maitang kisi in hong mu ngei ngawl lai te atu in deisakna lianpi ka nei na thu na heak tu uh ka dei hi;
\p 
\v 2 Tabang in amate thinsung sia henepna nga tu a, itna khau taw ki hen khawm in, Pa Pathian le Christ thuthuk heak theina tungtawn in a dim thinmuanna le hauna theampo na nei tu uh hi;
\p 
\v 3 Christ sungah ciimna le heakna i neisa te theampo sia ki phualseal hi.
\p 
\v 4 Kuama in theamna kammal te taw hong kaizot thei ngawl natu in hi thu kong son hi.
\p 
\v 5 Banghangziam cile ka pumpi taw note kungah ka om ngawl hang, thaa taw note kungah hong om khi hi, Christ sungah na upna uh a kip zia le na nuntak zia uh a hoi te en in ka lungdam hi.
\s1 Christ Sungah A Cialcing Nuntakna
\p 
\v 6 Tua ahikom note Topa Christ Jesus sang zo na hi uh bangma in, Ama sungah nungta vun:
\p 
\v 7 Ama sungah zungtha in, na nuntakna uh inn bang in sa tavun, upna sungah kho vun, hong ki hil sa bang in, tua thu sungah lungdamkona taw na kidim tavun.
\p 
\v 8 Khatpo in leitung ciimna le a mannung ngawl theamna te taw hong siatsua thei ngawl natu in kidawm vun, tua thu in mihing te i pulepa ngeina le leitung piancil pan ngeina hi a, Christ i ngeina bang hi ngawl hi.
\p 
\v 9 Banghang ziam cile Christ sungah Pathian hina kicing sia pumpi taw in om hi.
\p 
\v 10 Taciang note Christ sungah na kicing uh a, Ama sia thuneina le vangletna theampo i lutang a hihi.
\p 
\v 11 Note sia Christ sungah khut taw hi ngawl vunteap tan te na hi uh a, Christ vunteap tanna tungtawn in pumpi sungah cilesa khialna te na nusia siat zo uh hi:
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Rom 6:4\x*Tuiphumna sungah Ama taw a ki vui te na hi uh hi, taciang note mithi te kung pan Ama a thokiksak Pathian nasep na upna uh tungtawn in Ama taw na thokik zo uh hi.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Eph 2:1-5\x*Taciang na mawna te uh le na cilesa vunteap tan ngawl na sungah na thi uh laitak in, Ama taw hong nungtasak a, note i khialna theampo hong maisak hi;
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Eph 2:15\x*Eite langpang in khut taw a ki at biakna zeksa te sia eite taw ki lebul hi, taciang tua thu hong phiatsak a eite sung pan hong laksak in, Ama thinglamte tungah kilcip hi.
\p 
\v 15 Taciang thuneina te le vangletna te bosak hi, taciang a kilangtak in hong lak a, tua te i tungah thinglamte tungtawn in zo thal hi.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Rom 14:1-6\x*Tua ahikom neak le dawn huvau ahizong, ni le tha le sabbath ni thu huvau ahizong, kuama in note thu hong khen heak tahen:
\p 
\v 17 Tua bang te sia hong theng pheang tu thu te i lim a hihi; ahihang a pumpi sia Christ a hihi.
\p 
\v 18 A ki niamkhiak theam te le vantungmi te a bia te, a mu ngawl uh nate sungah tum uh a, a mannung ngawl cilesa thinsung taw a ki phasak peuma in na thaman uh hong theam heak tahen,
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Eph 4:16\x*Ama in lutang muang ngawl hi, tua lutang pan in ngu le tang te le thangui te tungtawn in pumpi buppi vaak hi, taciang khau bang in ki pheak khawm siat a, Pathian in khangtosak hi.
\p 
\v 20 Tua ahikom note leitung i bulpi thu te pan kipan in Christ taw na thi zo uh ahile, leitung ah a nungta bang in biakna ngeina thu te,
\p 
\v 21 (Tham heak vun; tep heak vun; len heak vun;
\p 
\v 22 Ta te theampo sia mangthang siat tu hi;) mihing te i thupiak te le updan te banghang in ni nu ziam?
\p 
\v 23 Tabang ngeina te sia cilesa lungkimna hi ngawl a, amate deina bang in biakna le ki niamkhiatna, taciang ama pumpi thusimngawlna taw pilna a ki langsak hi bek hi.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Ps 110:1\x*Note Christ taw na thokik khawm uh le, Christ to na Pathian ziatsang a om tungsang nate zong tavun.
\p 
\v 2 Leitung nate tung hi ngawl in, tunglam nate na thinsung uh ah koi vun.
\p 
\v 3 Banghangziam cile note sia na thi zo uh a, na nuntakna uh sia Christ taw Pathian sungah ki seal zo hi.
\p 
\v 4 Ka nuntakna uh a hi Christ hong kilang ciang in, note zong Ama taw minthanna sungah na kilang tu uh hi.
\s1 Nuntakna Lui le Nuntakna Thak
\p 
\v 5 Tua ahikom leitung ah a om na pumpikhen theampo; paktat na, thiantho ngawl na, ki tek thei ngawl lungngulna, cilesa deina, taciang duhopna a kici milim biakna te that siat vun:
\p 
\v 6 Banghangziam cile hi mawna te hang in thu ni ngawl tate tungah Pathian thin-ukna hong theng hi:
\p 
\v 7 Tua mawna te sungah na om uh lai in, note zong tua mawna te sungah na nungta ngei uh hi.
\p 
\v 8 Ahihang tu in hi thin-ukna, thangpaina, deisakna phangawl, sonsiatna, na kam uh sung pan kammal thiang ngawl theampo zong nusia vun.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Eph 4:22\x*Mihing lui le a nasep te nu sia siat zo na hi uh hu in khat le khat ki theam nawn heak vun;
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Eph 4:24; \xt Pian 1:26.\x*Taciang mi thak hina na sil zo uh hi, tasia in mihing thak a bitphua pa lim le meal bang in heakna sungah a ki thaksua a hihi.
\p 
\v 11 Tua sungah Greek le Judah, vunteap tan le tan ngawl, mimawl te, Scythian, sila le a suakta te, ci om ngawl hi: ahihang Christ sia na theampo hi a, na theampo sungah om hi.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Eph 4:2\x*Tua ahikom, Pathian hong tealna bang in, a thiangtho le a dei huai, hesuakna, phatna, thinsung ki niamkhiakna, nunneam le thinsauna te sil tavun;
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Eph 4:32\x*Khat le khat ki dual vun, khat le khat ki maisak vun, mi khatpo in ngualdang khat taw a ki hau le: Christ in note hong maisak bang in, note zong ki maisak tavun.
\p 
\v 14 Taciang hi te theampo tungah itna sil vun, tua itna in kicinna taw note hong hen khawm hi.
\p 
\v 15 Taciang Pathian i thinnopna in note i thinsung hong uk tahen, tabang hi tu in pumpi khat sungah hong sam khawm hi; lungdam ko thiam tavun.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Eph 5:19; 20\x*Note sungah Christ i kammal sia ciimna theampo taw hong dim tahen; hilna, khat le khat ki tek natu in Psalm la, pokna la le thaa la te na thinsung uh ah thuthiamna taw Topa tungah sa vun.
\p 
\v 17 Taciang na kampauna uh theampo, a hibale, na sep uh theampo te sia Topa Jesus min taw seam siat vun, Ama tungtawn in Pa Pathian tungah lungdam ko vun.
\s1 Tapidaw Innkuan
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Eph 5:22; 1 Pet 3:1\x*Zi te awng, Topa sungah a kilawm ahi bangma, na pasal te tungah noma le noma ki ap tavun.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Eph 5:25; 1 Pet 3:7\x*Pasal te awng, na zi te it vun, taciang amate langpan in ngoltol heak vun.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Eph 6:1\x*Ta te awng, na theampo ah na nu le na pa te thu ni vun: banghangziam cile hisia in Topa lungkimsak mama hi.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21 \xt Eph 6:4\x*Pa te awng, na tate uh thin-uksak heak vun, tabang a hibale, amate thinkiam tu hi.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt Eph 6:5-8\x*Sila te awng, cilesa ngeina bang in na to te thu sia, amate mitmuna ah mihing lungkimsak te bang bek hi ngawl in; Pathian zatakna taw na theampo ah thu ni vun:
\p 
\v 23 Bangpo na seam uh ahizong, na thinsung theampo taw, mihing te atu seam bang hi ngawl in, Topa atu seam bang in seam tavun;
\p 
\v 24 Topa kung pan na sep thaman ngamh na lua tu uh hi, ci he tavun: banghangziam cile note Topa Christ i na na seam uh hi.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 3:25 \xt Thuhlkk 10:17; Eph 6:9\x*Ahihang a man ngawl a seam te in a man ngawl a sepna thaman sangkik tu hi: taciang kuama doidanna om ngawl hi.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Eph 6:9\x*To te awng, note zong vantung ah To ka nei uh hi, ci he in, na sila te tungah a man le a kibang tek in pia vun.
\s1 Hanthotna
\p 
\v 2 Tatsat ngawl in thungen vun, taciang lungdamko kawm in ngak vun;
\p 
\v 3 Christ thuthuk hil tu in Pathian in kongkha hong honsak thei natu in, kote atu zong thu hong ngetsak tavun, tua a tu in keima sia thongtak ka hihi:
\p 
\v 4 Tabang in ka son tu a kilawm bang in ka pualak thei natu in, thu hong ngetsak tavun.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Eph 5:16\x*A puatham mite mai ah pilna taw nungta vun, hun zangthiam vun.
\p 
\v 6 Mihing khatsim sia bangbang in zo tu kilawm, ci na heak thei natu uh in, na kampauna uh a tawntung in thuthiamna taw hi tahen a, ci taw al tahen.
\s1 Akhakbel Nuksetna
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Sawl 20:4; 2 Tim 4:12\x*\x - \xo 4:7 \xt Eph 6:21, 22\x*Ka thu theampo sia Tychicus in hong hesak tu hi, ama sia i it suapui pa, a thuman naseam le Topa sungah ka nasep pui a hihi:
\p 
\v 8 Ama in note i zia le tong a heak thei natu le note hong henep thei natu ngealna taw, note kungah kong paisak a hihi;
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt Philm 1:10-12\x*Note sungah a thuman khat a hi, i it suapui pa, Onesimus taw kong paisak hi. Amate in hi mun ah thu piang te theampo hong son tu hi.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Sawl 19:29; 27:2; Philm 1:24; \xt Sawl 12:12,25; 13:13; 15:37-39.\x*Ka thongtak pui Aristarchus in hong paupui hi, taciang Barnabas tupa, Marcus in zong hong paupui hi, ama tung pan thupiak te na sang uh hi: note kung hongpai ahile, ama na sang vun;
\p 
\v 11 Taciang Justus a kici Jesus in zong hong paupui hi, amate sia vunteap tan te a hihi. Hite bekma Pathian kumpingam sungah ka nasep pui te hi a, keima hong heneam te a hihi.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Col 1:7; Philm 1:23\x*Note i sung pan mikhat, Christ i naseam, Epaphras in hong paupui hi, Pathian deina theampo sungah cialcing in, na khuagkhim thei natu uh in a tawntung in thinsung takpi taw thu hong ngetsak hi.
\p 
\v 13 Banghangziam cile ama in no Laodicea a omte le Hierapolis a omte atu in lawpna lian mama nei hi, ci sia keima in tetti ka pang hi.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt 2 Tim 4:11; Philm 1:24; \xt 2 Tim 4:10; Philm 1:24\x* I it mama syavuan Luke le Demas te in hong paupui hi.
\p 
\v 15 Laodicia a om suapui te ahizong, Nympha le a inn a om pawlpi te in ahizong, paupui vun.
\p 
\v 16 Taciang hi laithak sia noma sungah na sim zawk uh ciang in, Laodicea pawlpi te zong in sim tahen; taciang note zong Laodicea te kung pan laithak sia na sim vun.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Philm 1:2\x*Taciang Archippus kungah, Topa sungah na san nasep khuangkhim tu in ki nging in, ci na son vun.
\p 
\v 18 Keima Paul in paupuina sia ka khut taw ka at a hihi. Ka thongtakna na phawk nginge vun. Note tungah thuthiamna om tahen. Amen. 
